<ab facs="#facs_334_r1l30">auch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / daʒ der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>pet<ex>er</ex></expan> lucʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_334_line_1577278055447_1607"><expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſache </ab></add> nach dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_334_r1l31">als vns der pfıfferlıng <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> hett / an <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_334_r1l32">den <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex></expan> bracht vnd er Jm <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> hab . daʒ er hab </ab>
