<ab facs="#facs_334_r1l34"><expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Pfıfferlıng vnd wer des von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> gehabt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_334_r1l35">hab von der ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſıcher ſein <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd keins argen </ab>
