<pb facs="#facs_335" id="166v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l1"><expan>deſſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> mals auch <expan>ʒugeſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . als Jr an den <expan>abſchrıfte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l2">ʒweyr brıef <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan> / Des <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l3">vns ſeıd <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> vns auch des hinfür / Denn als Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l4">vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> Paulus <expan>wechſl<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l5"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır für vns beſandt vnd <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒurede geſacʒt / der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l6">hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> wıe vor <expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> ein knecht ʒu Jm keͣme </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l8">mıt rıngen dıe er Jm anpütte ʒu <expan>kawffe<ex>n</ex></expan> / dıe wölt er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_335_line_1577278087134_1638">auch </ab></add> nıht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l9">denn durchſlechts <expan>kawffe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo brecht Jm der knecht dıe rıng her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l10"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd geb Jm dıe durchſlechts ʒu kawffen . do ʒerflüg er ſıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l11">alſbald / daʒ es der knecht ſeͣhe / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> deẅht eẅch / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l12">
<add><ab facs="#facs_335_r1l1"><expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> ʒu dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Paulus <expan>wechſl<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> ıcht ʒu <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l13">hettet / ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vollen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l14">gewalt / <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l15">bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> wenn wır des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l16">ʒu den er ʒu <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett / anheim ſeyn <expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> Denn wo wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r2l17">eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_334" id="166r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
